cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper deals with visual search and query reformulation, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of generative adversarial models also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques for fashion and product search, which falls under computational linguistics (cs.CL).
